<title>USA: Sport-Haley seeks options to raise value.</title>
<headline>Sport-Haley seeks options to raise value.</headline>
<dateline>DENVER 1997-05-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Sport-Haley Inc on Friday said its board of directors has retained two investment banking firms to help it explore strategic options for increasing shareholder value.</p>
<p>The company said it has retained Donaldson Lufkin &amp; Jenrette Securities Corp and Dain Bosworth Inc.</p>
<p>Sport-Haley designs, contracts for the manufacture of, and markets men's and women's golf apparel under the Haley label.</p>
